metadata.name: He built for high
metadata.description:
Sun Yao always the eye is higher than top, dismissive to major woman, but whole cang yun door knows, he is infatuated with Gu Pan son very, also be acknowledged gu Pan son pursuer in actual strength is the strongest, most likely win fairy favour.



Sun Yao thought contemptuously: "What is this Ye Xiaochuan? Apart from being a disciple of Drunken master uncle, he was almost useless. Now only the "Yin and Yang Qiankun Dao" passed by cangyun Gate to the fourth level of god Sea realm, even the imperial sword flight did not reach. Also worthy of a crush on Paner?"
